name: SXZ Sylvanas Windrunner [ Warcraft ]
description:
All the content I make is and will be completely free on CivitAI.
But if you want to support me with a coin, then you can do it here.

Trained on AbyssOrangeMix2 with clip skip 2.

Recommended embeddings:
1. easynegative
2. bad-hands-5

Strength 0.6-0.8 is optimal.

PLEASE CHECK YOUR LORA NAME AFTER DOWNLOAD.

You may use sylvlight for Warcraft 3 or Reforged look (blue armor, blue eyes, blonde, ivory skin, alive) or sylvdark for look from World of Warcraft (purple armor, red eyes, ruined makeup, dark/pale skin, undead).

Use elf, long eyebrows, athletic for basic adjustments.

Also you may add blue eyes, hood on, blue armor, cleavage, midriff in positive prompt and makeup negative prompt for Ranger General (pre-Arthas) look.


And you may use colored skin, makeup, hood on, purple armor, cleavage in positive for Banshee Queen (post-Arthas) look.

Negative prompt: loli, kid, child, old

Please share your feedback.
